# The `VPBlockBase` Class Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/vpblockbase">VPBlockBase</a> is the building block of the Hierarchical Control-Flow Graph. <a href="#details">More...</a>

## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/vpblockbase">VPBlockBase</a> is the building block of the Hierarchical Control-Flow Graph.

A <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/vpblockbase">VPBlockBase</a> can be either a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/vpbasicblock">VPBasicBlock</a> or a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/vpregionblock">VPRegionBlock</a>.

Definition at line 392 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/transforms/lib/transforms/vectorize/vplan-h">VPlan.h</a>.

Print plain-text dump of this <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/vpblockbase">VPBlockBase</a> to <code>O</code>, prefixing all lines with <code>Indent</code>.

<code><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/slottracker">SlotTracker</a></code> is used to print unnamed <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/vpvalue">VPValue</a>&#39;s using consequtive numbers.

Note that the numbering is applied to the whole <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/vplan">VPlan</a>, so printing individual blocks is consistent with the whole <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/vplan">VPlan</a> printing.
